        "timestamp": "2017-09-06 12:18:52.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+2 Verified+1\n\nI'm okay with manually verifying this and fixing unit test in a separate change.  I think 2 of us will need to +1 Verified",
