        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(2 comments)\n\nFigured I would fix these test failures pre-merge after all.\n\nI also found that I needed to increment maven compile plugin version to 3.1+ to get this to compile locally. I wanted to see if jenkins build also required this as it seems to be have been compiling before enabling of unit tests.\n\npom.xml:\n...\n <properties>\n                <project.build.sourceEncoding>UTF-8</project.build.sourceEncoding>              <maven.compile.plugin.version>3.2</maven.compile.plugin.version>\n        </properties>\n...",
